  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Expected Output: An Allow header listing supported HTTP methods.",
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Security Implications: Unusual HTTP method support (PUT, DELETE) may indicate REST APIs or potential for HTTP method-based attacks.",
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "5.3 Proxy and Infrastructure Detection",
