  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Security Implications: Missing SameSite attribute increases vulnerability to CSRF attacks.",
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "6.4 Session Puzzling Testing",
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
